        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    actor Admin\n    participant UI as Next.js UI\n    participant API as FastAPI\n    participant DB as PostgreSQL\n \n    Admin-&gt;&gt;UI: Chon thang + lop, bam \&quot;Thiet lap thu thang moi\&quot;\n    UI-&gt;&gt;API: POST /fees/setup (period, class_id)\n    activate API\n    API-&gt;&gt;DB: SELECT enrollments chua co fee_record cho period\n    activate DB\n    DB--&gt;&gt;API: Danh sach enrollment_id + base_fee / custom_fee\n    deactivate DB\n    API--&gt;&gt;UI: Preview {to_create: N, skipped: M}\n    deactivate API\n    UI-&gt;&gt;Admin: Hien thi preview \&quot;Se tao N phieu, bo qua M\&quot;\n    Admin-&gt;&gt;UI: Bam Confirm\n    UI-&gt;&gt;API: POST /fees/setup/confirm\n    activate API\n    API-&gt;&gt;DB: INSERT fee_records (batch N rows)\n    activate DB\n    DB--&gt;&gt;API: OK - N rows inserted\n    deactivate DB\n    API--&gt;&gt;UI: {created: N}\n    deactivate API\n    UI-&gt;&gt;Admin: Toast \&quot;Da thiet lap N phieu hoc phi\&quot;\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="DzUow6_1HhxDGn1OBL8T-1">
